---
title: Savoury Apricot Chicken Tenders Stir-Fry with Buttered Rice
description: This mouth-watering chicken stir-fry has a secret ingredient: apricot spread. Tender chicken and veggies are coated in a sweet and savoury sauce, then nestled over top buttery basmati rice. Each bite is an explosion of flavour!
